-05-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110526055158/http://www.abc.net.au/foreign/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.frequency.com/video/abc-foreign-correspondent-on-thai/124233371/-/5-281801|title=Video: ABC Foreign Correspondent on the Thai monarchy ~ Frequency|date=2016-03-03|work=archive|accessdate=2017-05-18|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303232239/http://www.frequency.com/video/abc-foreign-correspondent-on-thai/124233371/-/5-281801|archivedate=2016-03-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>

